column2: (talent)-[:BELONGS_TO_WORKSPACE_SINCE]->(situation:HistoryItem)-[:RELATES_TO_WORKSPACE]->(workspace) WHERE (     situation.start <= $now     AND (situation.end IS NULL OR situation.end > $now) ) WITH DISTINCT principal
column7: CASE     WHEN (principal)-[:HAS_ADVANCED_ROLE_ON|HAS_ADMIN_ROLE_ON]->(workspace)      THEN [(contact:Contact)-[:BELONGS_TO]->(workspace) | contact.contactId]     ELSE       [] // in all other cases
column8: contacts are related to roles in the workspace     END as readeableContactsFromRole WITH principal
column12: CASE     WHEN (principal)-[:HAS_STANDARD_ROLE_ON]->(workspace) // only standards could have more contacts due to direct or indirect ownership      THEN         [(talent)<-[:RELATES_TO]-(contact:Contact)-[:BELONGS_TO]->(workspace) | contact.contactId]     ELSE       [] // in all other cases
column13: contacts are related to roles in the workspace     END as ownedContacts WITH readeableContactsFromRole
column15: [(account:Account)<-[:LINKED_TO]-(contact:Contact)     WHERE account.accountId in $accessibleAccountIds | contact.contactId ] as contactsLinkedToAccessibleAccount WITH readeableContactsFromRole + ownedContacts + contactsLinkedToAccessibleAccount as allAccessibleContacts UNWIND allAccessibleContacts as contactId RETURN DISTINCT contactId"
